
====== Installation ======

= System Installation
brew install watchman
npm install --global expo-cli
rm -rf node_modules
https://iterm2.com/
yarn add prop-types


==== Shortcut ======
ctrl-M for android
ctrl-D for IOS

Create a new expo project
expo init Duolingo -t blank

======== React native =======
Text, View, Image, ScrollView, TextInput

- <View> Some text components </View>

- <Text>Hello World!</Text>
  properties:
     numberOfLines={2}
     ellipsizeMode="head, tail"

- ScrollView basically, enclose everything you want to scroll inside

- <Image
      source={{name or uri: "https://iterm2.com/"}},
      style={{ width:100, height: 100 }} resizeMode="cover, contain"
   />

- <TextInput />

========= Styling =======

style={{ height: 100}} inline styling

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
   root: {
   }
})
style={ styles.root }

The style can be in the separated folder
import as an array

